<P>
<B>
Nuclear Power Performance and Safety
<BR>
<I>Proceedings Series</I>
</B>
<P>
Proceedings of a conference, Vienna, 28 September to 2 October
1987. These proceedings provide an authoritative and
comprehensive picture of the current status of and trends in
nuclear power, nuclear safety and the nuclear fuel cycle.
<P>
<DL>
