aspects of the economic evaluation of financing proposals;
Implementation of the economic bid evaluation; Technology
transfer;
Appendix A. IAEA account system for nuclear power plants;
Appendix
B. Example of sensitivity analysis; Appendix C. Abbreviations;
Annex: IAEA computer programme for economic bid evaluation;
Bibliography.
