<BR>
ISBN 92-0-125386-9
<BR>
Price: 480 Austrian Schillings
<P>
<B>
Nuclear Power Plant Availability, Maintenance and Operation 
<BR>
<I>Proceedings Series</I>
</B>
<P>
Proceedings of a symposium, Munich, Germany, 20-23 May 1985. The
purpose of the meeting was to review advances in nuclear power
plant availability resulting from improvements in plant design,
construction practices, plant operation and maintenance, new
operation management schemes and the development of effective
nuclear power regulations.
<P>
<I>Contents:</I> Operation information systems; Advances in
design
and plant systems and components; Advances in materials and
methods; Advances in maintenance; Regulatory controls on
operation;
Advances in management and operation; Manpower requirements and
training; Panels: 1. Preventive maintenance and backfitting of
nuclear power plants; 2. Quality assurance in nuclear power plant
operation and maintenance.
