<B><A NAME=624>
Conditioning of Radioactive Wastes for Storage and Disposal  
<BR>
<I>Proceedings Series</I>
</B></A>
<P>
Proceedings of a symposium jointly sponsored with CEC and
OECD/NEA, Utrecht, Netherlands, 21-25 June 1982. The papers and
discussions provide an authoritative account of the status of
conditioning of a wide variety of wastes, including spent ion
exchange resins, incinerator ash, high level and long lived
