<B><A NAME=940>
Radioactive Waste Management Glossary
</B></A>
<P>
The purpose of this glossary is to provide a source of words
which are commonly and internationally used or have special
meanings in the field of radioactive waste management. It should
further contribute to a common use of terms in the IAEA
Radioactive Waste Safety Standards (RADWASS) series. In the
context of this glossary, the term `waste' refers, in general, to
radioactive waste unless otherwise specified.
