needs and techniques for site evaluation; 7. Application of earth
science investigative studies; 8. Other studies; 9. Conclusions;
Appendix A. Synopsis of national activities on investigations for
deep geological repository sites as of May 1980; Appendix B.
Summary of principal hydrogeological testing methods; Appendix C.
Summary of geophysical log applications for repository site
investigations; Appendix D. Field geotechnical tests and
measurements; Appendix E. Principal laboratory geomechanical
testing methods; References; Bibliography; Glossary.
