<P>
This document is a follow-up report to IAEA Safety Series No. 59,
Disposal of Low and Intermediate Level Solid Radioactive Wastes
in Rock Cavities -- A Guidebook, which reviewed and gave general
guidelines on the subject. The present publication is more
technical in its approach.
