<BR>
<I>Safety Series No.
111-G-3.1</I>
</B></A>
<P>
This Safety Guide defines the site selection process and criteria
for identifying suitable near surface disposal facilities. It
provides guidelines for the siting process management and
specifies the data needed to apply the relevant selection
criteria.
<P>
<I>Contents:</I> 1. Introduction; 2. Approach to siting; 3.
Management of the siting process; 4. Siting guidelines and data
needs.
<P>
STI/PUB/965 (37 pp.; 1994)
