and gas cleaning systems; Testing of particulate filters and
systems; Iodine sorption system testing; Noble gas delay system
testing; Process control and performance monitoring; Criteria for
testing of gas cleaning systems; Trends and development of
testing and monitoring; Summary and conclusions; Appendix.
