<B>
Energy from Inertial Fusion
</B>
<P>
This publication describes the current scientific, engineering
and technological developments in the field of inertial
confinement fusion (ICF).  It provides an introduction to ICF as
well as an overview of the various technologies needed for
inertial fusion power plant development.  It was compiled by an
international group of experts under the auspices of an IAEA
Advisory Group on Inertial Fusion Energy and is intended for a
large audience, e.g. policy makers, scientists, engineers or
technologists in other fields, and students.
