<P>
The publication contains the most important treaties, agreements
and conventions in the field of arms control and disarmament.
<P>
STI/PUB/387 (78 pp.; 1975)
<BR>
ISBN 92-0-176075-2
<BR>
Price: 120 Austrian Schillings
<P>
<B>
Licensing and Regulatory Control
of Nuclear Installations
<BR>
<I>Legal Series No. 10</I>
</B>
<P>
A selection of papers presented at a Regional Seminar in Nuclear
Law for Latin American Countries, Rio de Janeiro, 25-29 June
1973, and at the Study Group Meeting on Regulations and
