<I>Proceedings Series</I></B> 
<P>
Proceedings of a symposium jointly organized with the Commission
of the European Communities and the OECD Nuclear Energy Agency
and held in Knoxville, Tennessee, 27-31 July 1981. Among the
various radionuclides arising from the nuclear fuel cycle, those
