<H2>
Nuclear Measurements, Techniques and Instrumentation
</H2>
<H3>NUCLEAR DATA</H3>
<P>
</CENTER>
<P>
<HR>
<P>
<B>CINDA 96 - Supplement to CINDA 95 (1988-1996)</B>
<P>
CINDA 96 is the supplement to CINDA 95, an index to the literature on neutron nuclear data published after 1987. The complete CINDA file as of 1 June 1996 is contained in the archival issue CINDA-A (5 volumes, 1990) plus CINDA 95 and the current issue CINDA 96. 
