<DOCNO>WT19-B40-54</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA059-000323-B011-35</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://nesihp01.iaea.or.at:80/worldatom/inforesource/annual/anrep95/box2.html 193.81.60.210 19970114214742 text/html 3077
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
