<TD>For the INTERNATIONAL ATOMIC<BR>ENERGY AGENCY:</TD>
</TR>
<TR>
<TD>(signed) S. Tereshchenko</TD>
<TD>(signed) Hans Blix</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>
</CENTER>
