A Communication Dated 28 June 1996 from the Permanent Mission of
Sweden</H3></CENTER>
<P>
<OL>
<LI>The Director General of the IAEA received a note verbale of
28 June 1996 from the Permanent Mission of
Sweden about the adoption, by the Government of Sweden, of the
common policy declaration adopted on 20
November 1984 by the ministers for foreign affairs of the then
ten members of the European Community. This was
transmitted to the Director General by the Resident
Representative of Italy on behalf of the Community on
22 March 1985 and is reproduced in <A
