Minister of Foreign Affairs
<BR>
(Title)
<P>	
Bridgetown 14 August 1996
<BR>
(Place) (Date)</TD>
<TD>For the INTERNATIONAL  ATOMIC 	ENERGY AGENCY:
<P>
