adjacent metal structures and cables within or above the roof
line <I>incl.</I>  all bends, joints, clips and fixings.
<P>
<DD>Discharge devices (protective gaps) to aerials and similar
equipment.
<P>
<DD>Down conductor strips, bonding connections to adjacent metal
structures, dissimilar metal contact isolators (aluminum/copper)
and all bends, joints, clips  and fixings.
<P>
<DD>Earth termination electrodes and bonding connections to
service and waste pipework and fittings within "flashover" zone.
<P>
<DD>Earth electrode access covers and surrounds.
</DL>
