<HEAD>
<TITLE>INFCIRC/153 (Corrected)</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR=#FFFFFF>
<TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=100%>
<TR>
<TD ALIGN=left>
<IMG SRC="/worldatom/images/iaeasmal.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="IAEA Logo">
<BR>
<B>International Atomic Energy Agency</B>
